
---

# 2️⃣ .gitignore

Open `.gitignore` and replace with this:

```gitignore
# dependencies
/node_modules

# next.js build output
/.next/
/out/

# production
/build

# logs
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

# environment variables
.env*
.env.local
.env.development.local
.env.test.local
.env.production.local

# vercel
.vercel

# typescript
*.tsbuildinfo
next-env.d.ts

# macOS
.DS_Store

# windows
Thumbs.db

# vscode
.vscode

# misc
*.log